General.Name: Openn Negotiation Ltd
General.Description: Openn Negotiation Limited operates as a property technology company in Australia, New Zealand, and the United States. It offers a cloud-based software platform to support real estate agents in selling property online by facilitating the negotiation process, streamlining digital contracting, and automating communication tools that enhances property transactions. Openn Negotiation Limited was formerly known as Appwell Pty Ltd. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Claremont, Australia.
